OL,6,FA mother and her two young children
OL,7,Fwho died in a house fire on Boxing Day
OL,8,Fhave been named locally.
OL,10,FFionnghuala Shearman, known as Nu,
OL,11,Fdied alongside her children, Eve, aged
OL,12,Fseven, and four-year-old son Ohner in
OL,13,Fthe fire which broke out in the early
OL,14,Fhours of 26 December at the family
OL,15,Fhome near Stroud.
OL,17,FThe father and husband attempted to
OL,18,Frescue his family but was beaten back
OL,19,Fby the severity of the fire that
OL,20,Fdestroyed his home in Brimscombe, near
OL,21,FStroud, Gloucestershire.
