OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference on 30
OL,7,FDecember, temporary Chief Constable of
OL,8,FGloucestershire Police Maggie Blyth
OL,9,Fprovided an update and thanked the
OL,10,Flocal community for its support.
OL,12,FShe confirmed that the recovery and
OL,13,Fremoval of the bodies of the mother,
OL,14,Fthe children and the family dog have
OL,15,Fnow taken place.
