OL,6,F"I want to take this opportunity to
OL,7,Fthank those agencies that have worked
OL,8,Fwith the constabulary. Namely the fire
OL,9,Fservice and local authorities and
OL,10,Fvoluntary sector for the enduring
OL,11,Finvestigations they've been part of
OL,12,Fover the last few days.
OL,14,F"I (also) want to thank our
OL,15,Fcommunities in Gloucestershire that
OL,16,Fhave shown me and my officers huge
OL,17,Fcompassion and kindness over the last
OL,18,F24 hours", she added.
