OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Ffamily's mid-terrace Cotswold stone
OL,8,Fcottage on Brimscombe Hill at about
OL,9,F3am on Boxing Day.
OL,11,FDetective Superintendent Ian Fletcher
OL,12,Fsaid the mother and father were woken
OL,13,Fby the fire and had attempted to reach
OL,14,Ftheir children in the rear bedroom,
OL,15,Fbut were unable to get there due to
OL,16,Fthe ferocity of the fire.
OL,18,F"The father has smashed his way out of
OL,19,Fthe house through a bathroom window in
OL,20,Forder to try to access the children's
OL,21,Fbedroom via the outside", he said.
