OL,6,F"He has been unable to enter the
OL,7,Fproperty via that bedroom window.
OL,9,F"He has then tried to re-enter the
OL,10,Fproperty through the bathroom window,
OL,11,Fby which stage the fire has taken hold
OL,12,Fin the bathroom and he's unable to get
OL,13,Fback into the upstairs bedrooms.
OL,15,F"He has subsequently gone downstairs
OL,16,Fand tried to force entry via the front
OL,17,Fand the back door but has been unable
OL,18,Fto get back inside to the property.
