OL,6,F"It is at this point our colleagues
OL,7,Ffrom emergency services have attended
OL,8,Fand have started managing and dealing
OL,9,Fwith that fire."
OL,11,FMr Fletcher said the fire was believed
OL,12,Fto have started on the ground floor
OL,13,Fand investigations were ongoing to
OL,14,Festablish the cause but it was not
OL,15,Fbeing treated as suspicious.
OL,17,FThe fire destroyed the roof, the
OL,18,Fceilings and stairs, as well as
OL,19,Fcausing other significant internal
OL,20,Fdamage.
